    "description": {
      "value": "<h2></b>Description</b></h2></p><p>This whetstone is made from finely worked obsidian. Sharpening a blade with this whetstone requires 15 minutes of work and grants the weapon the ability to ignore up to 3 points of natural armor for its next five attacks. If the target of the weapon's attack has a natural armor bonus of less than +3, the weapon deals 1 additional point of damage for each point of natural armor below 3 the target has. The process of honing the blade shatters a portion of the whetstone's enchanted obsidian, dispelling its magic and turning it into a mundane whetstone afterward.<br><p><b>Base Item:</b> </p><h3><b>Requirements</b></h3><p>Craft Wondrous Item, keen edge</p><h3><b>Source: </b></h3>Monster Hunter's Handbook",
